OL,3,CMidlands councils request election
OL,4,Cdelay amid reorganisation plans
OL,6,FCouncil leaders in parts of the
OL,7,FMidlands have asked the Government to
OL,8,Fpostpone local elections scheduled for
OL,9,FMay 2025.
OL,11,FThe request forms part of plans for
OL,12,Fthe most significant reorganisation of
OL,13,Flocal government in decades. The
OL,14,FGovernment is seeking to abolish two-
OL,15,Ftier council systems to devolve more
OL,16,Fpower from Westminster to local
OL,17,Fauthorities.
