OL,3,CMidlands councils request election
OL,4,Cdelay amid reorganisation plans
OL,6,FSix midlands councils have made the
OL,7,Frequest. They are Derbyshire,
OL,8,FGloucestershire, Leicestershire,
OL,9,FLincolnshire, Warwickshire,
OL,10,FWorcestershire.
OL,12,FThe Ministry of Housing, Communities
OL,13,Fand Local Government has confirmed it
OL,14,Fhas received requests from multiple
OL,15,Fcouncils to delay elections until 2026.
OL,17,FBut what does it mean for people
OL,18,Facross the Midlands?
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
