OL,3,CMidlands councils request election
OL,4,Cdelay amid reorganisation plans
OL,6,FWell, local government minister Jim
OL,7,FMcMahon told MPs that any decision to
OL,8,Fdelay elections will be made carefully.
OL,10,FHe said: "Where local elections are
OL,11,Fpostponed, we'll work with local areas
OL,12,Fto move elections to a new shadow
OL,13,Funitary council as soon as possible.
OL,14,FThis is a very high bar, and rightly
OL,15,Fso."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
