OL,3,CMidlands councils request election
OL,4,Cdelay amid reorganisation plans
OL,6,FMcMahon added that not all areas
OL,7,Frequesting delays will be approved,
OL,8,Fbut the Government would consider
OL,9,Fsubmissions where there is a clear
OL,10,Fcommitment to reorganisation and
OL,11,Fdevolution within an ambitious
OL,12,Ftimeline.
OL,14,FShadow communities minister David
OL,15,FSimmonds raised concerns over the
OL,16,Funcertainty, warning it could lead to
OL,17,Fwasted costs for council taxpayers if
OL,18,Felections proceed as planned.
