OL,6,FLiberal Democrat local government
OL,7,Fspokeswoman Vikki Slade criticised
OL,8,Faspects of the Government's approach,
OL,9,Fdescribing it as a potential "top-down
OL,10,Fdiktat from Whitehall." She also
OL,11,Fclaimed that some councils were not
OL,12,Ffully consulted before requests for
OL,13,Felection delays were submitted.
OL,15,FThe Government has yet to announce its
OL,16,Ffinal decision, with further updates
OL,17,Fexpected in due course.
